overview: It all starts when Rea invites her boyfriend Zacky (Iqbal Rizantha) to play jelangkung. Her friend scold at her for doing this but it is too late, calamity already begins. A spirit is haunting them and Rea tries to find a way to get rid of it. They go to see a paranormal, and they are told that the only way to get rid of the spirit is by pulling up a jelangkung doll that is planted one year ago in Angker Batu.
tagline: Datang tak dijemput, pulang tak diantar
title: Tusuk Jelangkung
